            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/379932-anna-kendig?shelf=chaplain-ish-things">chaplain-ish-things</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer161070114" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer164451184355244502">Really useful as a reflection tool with parish care teams or just for anyone who wants to think about how to be with people who are going through difficult times. Offers impressions from professionals in the non-profit, therapeutic and ministerial fields as well as just general suggestions like a what not to say/what&apos;s better&quot; grid that offers better options than saying &quot;Maybe it&apos;s for the best&quot; to someone who&apos;s in a difficult place. Highly readable.</span>
  <span id="freeText164451184355244502" style="display:none">Really useful as a reflection tool with parish care teams or just for anyone who wants to think about how to be with people who are going through difficult times. Offers impressions from professionals in the non-profit, therapeutic and ministerial fields as well as just general suggestions like a what not to say/what's better" grid that offers better options than saying "Maybe it's for the best" to someone who's in a difficult place. Highly readable.</span>
  <a data-text-id="164451184355244502" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
