        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2521318292" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer1798866424483041333">This is a very useful book, with a lot of excellent information. The reason I’m only giving it 3 stars is because it turns a bit formulaic, and often belabors somewhat obvious points. It is a calming book, and points out a lot which ought to be obvious, but may not be. Overall I’d recommend it if you are interested in the topic, but give the caveat of needing to push through a bit. Also, I didn’t personally feel like the section on comforting things was necessary, as that is going at change pers</span>
  <span id="freeText1798866424483041333" style="display:none">This is a very useful book, with a lot of excellent information. The reason I’m only giving it 3 stars is because it turns a bit formulaic, and often belabors somewhat obvious points. It is a calming book, and points out a lot which ought to be obvious, but may not be. Overall I’d recommend it if you are interested in the topic, but give the caveat of needing to push through a bit. Also, I didn’t personally feel like the section on comforting things was necessary, as that is going at change person to person. But maybe others would find it useful. Happy reading!</span>
  <a data-text-id="1798866424483041333" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

